---
title: Hover Dropdown Menu
description: A navigation dropdown that opens on hover using `:hover` and `visibility`.
slug: hover-dropdown
cssFile: hover-dropdown.css
explanation: <code>visibility:hidden</code> + <code>opacity:0</code> hides the menu while keeping it in the layout flow for transitions. <code>opacity</code> alone can't be transitioned to/from <code>display:none</code>. Using <code>visibility</code> allows a transition on <code>opacity</code>, then <code>visibility</code> jumps to hidden after the fade completes. The parent <code>:hover</code> selector reveals the child menu.
---
{% extends "example.njk" %}
{% block demo %}
<div style="display:flex;gap:1.5rem;padding-bottom:140px">
	<div class="dropdown">
		<span class="dropdown-trigger">
			Products
			<svg class="dropdown-arrow" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
		</span>
		<div class="dropdown-menu">
			<a href="#">Web Design</a>
			<a href="#">Mobile Apps</a>
			<a href="#">Branding</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="dropdown">
		<span class="dropdown-trigger">
			Resources
			<svg class="dropdown-arrow" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
		</span>
		<div class="dropdown-menu">
			<a href="#">Documentation</a>
			<a href="#">Blog</a>
			<a href="#">Support</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
{% endblock %}

{% block html_code %}
{%- highlight "html" %}
<div class="dropdown">
  <span class="dropdown-trigger">Menu</span>
  <div class="dropdown-menu">
    <a href="#">Item one</a>
    <a href="#">Item two</a>
  </div>
</div>
{%- endhighlight %}
{% endblock %}

{% block css_code %}
{%- highlight "css" %}
.dropdown { position: relative; display: inline-block; }

.dropdown-menu {
  position: absolute;
  top: calc(100% + 6px);
  left: 0;
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid #e2e2e8;
  border-radius: 8px;
  opacity: 0;
  visibility: hidden;
  transform: translateY(-6px);
  transition: opacity .2s, transform .2s, visibility .2s;
}

.dropdown:hover .dropdown-menu {
  opacity: 1;
  visibility: visible;
  transform: translateY(0);
}
{%- endhighlight %}
{% endblock %}
